  "description": "Low tangle (0.35) on the figure-eight preserves the sense of two distinct loops — like two voices walking parallel paths. Long 32ms delay base creates a thick, low-register feel. High diffusion at 0.7 and heavy dampening wash the high frequencies into a dark, warm haze. Very long release (7s).",
